  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK155">
<l>oṟuttārai yoṉṟāka vaiyārē vaippar</l>
<l>poṟuttāraip poṉpōṟ potintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The wise) will not at all esteem the resentful. They will esteem the patient just as the gold which they lay up with care.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
